parts: Make up a 5-sentence story about "Sharky", a tooth-brushing shark superhero. Make each sentence a bullet point.

- Sharky, the fearless tooth-brushing shark superhero, roams the ocean depths, fighting against the evil plaque monsters that threaten marine creatures' smiles.  
- Armed with his electrified toothbrush and minty-fresh toothpaste, he zooms through the waves, cleaning up cavities and saving sea animals from painful dental decay.  
- One day, the villainous King Tartar rises from the dark trenches, plotting to cover the entire ocean floor with sticky plaque.  
- Sharky, with his pearly white grin, dives into action, brushing through the villainâ€™s defenses and polishing the coral reefs to sparkle again.  
- With King Tartar defeated, Sharky becomes a hero across the seas, reminding everyone that a clean mouth leads to a healthy smile!
